THE PRESIDENT TOUCHED ON VOTER

01:08.035 --> 01:09.670
APATHY, PROTESTS IN FERGUSON,

01:09.670 --> 01:11.705
AND THE HISTORICAL IMPORTANCE OF

01:11.705 --> 01:13.273
THE MARCH ON SELMA.

01:13.273 --> 01:14.074
>> THE AMERICANS WHO CROSSED

01:14.074 --> 01:15.442
THIS BRIDGE, THEY WERE NOT

01:15.442 --> 01:17.711
PHYSICALLY IMPOSING, BUT THEY

01:17.711 --> 01:21.615
GAVE COURAGE TO MILLIONS.

01:21.615 --> 01:24.851
THEY HELD NO ELECTED OFFICE, BUT

01:24.851 --> 01:26.353
THEY LED A NATION.

01:26.353 --> 01:30.057
BECAUSE OF WHAT THEY DID, THE

01:30.057 --> 01:31.758
DOORS OF OPPORTUNITY SWUNG OPEN

01:31.758 --> 01:33.593
NOT JUST FOR BLACK FOLKS, BUT

01:33.593 --> 01:36.563
FOR EVERY AMERICAN.

01:36.563 --> 01:37.597
WOMEN MARCHED THROUGH THOSE

01:37.597 --> 01:38.799
DOORS.

01:38.799 --> 01:40.000
LATINOS MARCHED THROUGH THOSE

01:40.000 --> 01:41.134
DOORS.

01:41.134 --> 01:43.603
ASIAN-AMERICANS, GAY AMERICANS,

01:43.603 --> 01:45.339
AMERICANS WITH DISABILITIES,

01:45.339 --> 01:46.740
THEY ALL CAME THROUGH THOSE

01:46.740 --> 01:47.841
DOORS.

01:47.841 --> 01:48.875
WHAT HAPPENED IN FERGUSON MAY

01:48.875 --> 01:50.143
NOT BE UNIQUE, BUT IT'S NO

01:50.143 --> 01:52.512
LONGER ENDEMIC OR SANCTIONED BY

01:52.512 --> 01:54.748
LAW AND CUSTOM; AND BEFORE THE

01:54.748 --> 01:56.183
CIVIL RIGHTS MOVEMENT, IT MOST

01:56.183 --> 01:57.718
SURELY WAS.

01:57.718 --> 01:59.419
WHAT'S OUR EXCUSE TODAY FOR NOT

01:59.419 --> 02:01.922
VOTING?

02:01.922 --> 02:03.657
HOW DO WE SO CASUALLY DISCARD

02:03.657 --> 02:05.592
THE RIGHT FOR WHICH SO MANY

02:05.592 --> 02:08.095
FOUGHT?

02:08.095 --> 02:09.629
HOW DO WE SO FULLY GIVE AWAY OUR

02:09.629 --> 02:11.698
POWER, OUR VOICE, IN SHAPING

02:11.698 --> 02:12.833
AMERICA'S FUTURE?

02:12.833 --> 02:13.667
>> Sreenivasan: GEORGIA

