02:42.429 --> 02:43.897
PICTURE, THE MARCH THAT IS

02:43.897 --> 02:46.066
SEARED IN PEOPLE'S MINDS.

02:46.066 --> 02:47.067
WHAT KIND OF CHANGES HAPPENED

02:47.067 --> 02:48.201
SINCE THEN, ESPECIALLY FOR

02:48.201 --> 02:49.569
VOTING RIGHTS?

