>> WELL, FIRST OF ALL, YOU'VE

02:51.071 --> 02:54.341
SEEN A COMPLETE COLLAPSE OF

02:54.341 --> 02:56.076
REPUBLICAN SUPPORT AMONG AFRICAN

02:56.076 --> 02:56.543
AMERICANS.

02:56.543 --> 02:58.412
THAT HAPPENED VERY QUICKLY.

02:58.412 --> 02:59.513
RICHARD NIXON GOT ABOUT A THIRD

02:59.513 --> 03:01.615
OF THE BLACK VOTE IN 1960.

03:01.615 --> 03:03.450
BARRY GOLDWATER GOT 6%.

03:03.450 --> 03:04.484
REPUBLICANS HAVE NEVER

03:04.484 --> 03:05.752
APPROACHED THAT NIXON LEVEL

03:05.752 --> 03:07.454
SINCE.

03:07.454 --> 03:09.990
SECOND, YOU'VE HAD BLACKS AND

03:09.990 --> 03:11.625
NON-WHITES IN GENERAL, INCLUDING

03:11.625 --> 03:13.760
HISPANICS AND LATINOS, EXPAND AS

03:13.760 --> 03:15.595
A PROPORTION OF THE ELECTORATE.

03:15.595 --> 03:17.964
AND OVER TIME, THAT HAS WORKED

03:17.964 --> 03:18.732
TO THE ADVANTAGE OF THE

03:18.732 --> 03:20.600
DEMOCRATIC PARTY.

03:20.600 --> 03:21.868
1964, WHEN LYNDON JOHNSON WAS

03:21.868 --> 03:23.770
RE-ELECTED, WHITES PROVIDED

03:23.770 --> 03:26.206
ABOUT 95% OF ALL THE VOTES CAST

03:26.206 --> 03:27.441
IN THE ELECTION.

03:27.441 --> 03:31.678
IN 2012, WHITES WERE ABOUT 72%,

03:31.678 --> 03:34.448
AND THAT GROWTH, GIVEN THE

03:34.448 --> 03:36.349
SHIFT OF WHITES TO VERY

03:36.349 --> 03:38.385
DOMINANT SUPPORT FOR THE

03:38.385 --> 03:41.154
REPUBLICAN PARTY, NON-WHITES FOR

03:41.154 --> 03:42.522
THE DEMOCRATIC PARTY, HAS

03:42.522 --> 03:44.157
PRODUCED A RACIALLY POLARIZED

03:44.157 --> 03:45.559
ELECTORATE, BUT ONE THAT, GIVEN

03:45.559 --> 03:47.694
THE GROWTH OF NON-WHITES, HAS

03:47.694 --> 03:48.662
WORKED TO THE DEMOCRATS'

03:48.662 --> 03:49.563
ADVANTAGE IN PRESIDENTIAL

03:49.563 --> 03:50.363
ELECTIONS LATELY.

