REPUBLICANS HAVE BECOME ALMOST

04:38.311 --> 04:40.614
ENTIRELY A CONSERVATIVE PARTY,

04:40.614 --> 04:42.949
DEMOCRATS LEFT OF CENTER, AND

04:42.949 --> 04:44.918
THAT IS THE... THOSE ARE THE

04:44.918 --> 04:47.020
CONTOURS THAT THEY'RE GOING TO

04:47.020 --> 04:48.054
RESUME WHEN THEY GET BACK TO

04:48.054 --> 04:48.855
WASHINGTON.

04:48.855 --> 04:50.257
>> Sreenivasan: HOW HAVE SOME OF

04:50.257 --> 04:51.324
THE RECENT EVENTS-- THE 2013

