WITH DIGNITY LAW."

14:01.274 --> 14:02.108
>> Reporter: UNDER OREGON'S LAW,

14:02.108 --> 14:03.576
A DOCTOR MUST DETERMINE A

14:03.576 --> 14:05.511
TERMINALLY ILL PATIENT HAS SIX

14:05.511 --> 14:07.613
MONTHS OR FEWER TO LIVE.

14:07.613 --> 14:09.182
THE PHYSICIAN CAN WRITE A LIFE-

14:09.182 --> 14:11.184
ENDING PRESCRIPTION ONLY AFTER A

14:11.184 --> 14:13.486
SECOND DOCTOR SIGNS ON AND BOTH

14:13.486 --> 14:15.121
AGREE THE PATIENT IS OF SOUND

14:15.121 --> 14:16.289
MIND.

14:16.289 --> 14:17.557
THE PATIENT MUST REQUEST THE

14:17.557 --> 14:19.959
DRUG AGAIN 15 DAYS AFTER THE

14:19.959 --> 14:21.627
INITIAL REQUEST.

14:21.627 --> 14:23.329
BUT ONCE THE PATIENT HAS IT, THE

14:23.329 --> 14:25.198
DOCTORS' ROLE IS OVER.

14:25.198 --> 14:26.966
SINCE THE LAW WENT INTO EFFECT

14:26.966 --> 14:30.236
IN 1997, OVER 1,300 PEOPLE HAVE

14:30.236 --> 14:31.437
RECEIVED LIFE-ENDING

14:31.437 --> 14:34.574
PRESCRIPTIONS, BUT JUST 859 HAVE

14:34.574 --> 14:36.843
ACTUALLY TAKEN THEM AND DIED.

14:36.843 --> 14:38.611
OTHERS DIED SOONER AND SOME

14:38.611 --> 14:40.413
CHANGED THEIR MINDS.

14:40.413 --> 14:42.448
AS BEN'S HEALTH DETERIORATED, HE

14:42.448 --> 14:44.050
AND PAM SOUGHT HELP FROM

14:44.050 --> 14:45.585
COMPASSION AND CHOICES, THE

14:45.585 --> 14:47.019
GROUP THAT SUPPORTED BRITTANY

14:47.019 --> 14:48.054
MAYNARD.

14:48.054 --> 14:49.789
IN 2012, THE GROUP CONNECTED

14:49.789 --> 14:51.891
THEM WITH TWO DOCTORS WHO SIGNED

14:51.891 --> 14:53.659
